From: Sidhant Goel <sidhant@hexcod.in>
Date: Tue, 18 Nov 2025 15:04:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] phy: aquantia: defer probe on firmware mtd not ready

Signed-off-by: Sidhant Goel <sidhant@hexcod.in>
---
 drivers/net/phy/aquantia/aquantia_firmware.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/phy/aquantia/aquantia_firmware.c b/drivers/net/phy/aquantia/aquantia_firmware.c
index dab3af80593f..05a90cc030ad 100644
--- a/drivers/net/phy/aquantia/aquantia_firmware.c
+++ b/drivers/net/phy/aquantia/aquantia_firmware.c
@@ -371,6 +371,9 @@ int aqr_firmware_load(struct phy_device *phydev)
 		if (!ret)
 			return ret;
 
+		if(ret == -EPROBE_DEFER) 
+			return ret;
+
 		ret = aqr_firmware_load_fs(phydev);
 		if (ret)
 			return ret;
